<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body>
<div style="font-family: Microsoft JhengHei, 'Lato', Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; padding: 5px 20px;	">	
<div style="font-weight: bold; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 10px; width: 170px; border: 2px solid #198EB9;color: #198EB9;	">
	<div style="margin-left: 12%; 
				width: 80%; 
				line-height: 13px; 
				letter-spacing: 7px; 
				font-size: 10px; 
				text-align: center;	">EasyRegister 報名系統</div>	
</div>	
<div style="letter-spacing: 1.5px;
		    padding-bottom: 30px; 
		    padding-top: 10px; 	
		    padding-left: 5px; 		    	    
		    border-bottom: 1px solid #198EB9; 
		    border-top: 1px solid #198EB9; 
		    margin-bottom: 30px;">		
<div class="masonry" style="-moz-column-count: 4;
						    -webkit-column-count: 4;
						    column-count: 4;
						    -moz-column-gap: 1em;
						    -webkit-column-gap: 1em;
						    column-gap: 1em;">
<%=@progress.user.name%> 您好!
<br>   
<b><%=@progress.period.group.title%></b>
審核不通過/取消資格 原因: <%=@progress.reason%><br>
需要您重新送出報名申請，請點擊以下連結進行動作。
<br>
<%= host+Hash[controllerOptions].rassoc(@progress.period.group.system_module.serial_code).first+'/'+Hash[stageOptions].rassoc(@progress.stage).first+'?id='+@progress.period.id%>    
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
		
</body>
</html>